I've been going to this barely visible coffee shop for almost ten years and it is one of the better ones. It is small and the crowd is mostly teens, but the coffee is good. They use Illy espresso beans which is rich and delicious. Their menu is simple with about 5 specialty drinks. I would definitely recommend the French Caramel Latte. It has a nutty flavor that goes great with the caramel.

