I am a Yogurtland addict. Sometimes I have it as a meal. I've tried Pinkberry, Yogurtberry, Mojo, etc but nothing compares! Yogurtland has a wide selection of flavors...including some exotic Asian flavors such as Lychee and Taro (my fav). There's also a new flavor that comes out every few weeks. The add ons are pretty standard, but they have a more syrups than other yogurt shops. The fruits are fresh.

